        story: `"I haven't slept well, crew. A storm keeps building in my dreams, and I have this feeling — the kind Hina says wayfinders learn to trust — that it's not just a dream. Before it arrives, our sails need to be strong enough to use the wind, not be torn apart by it. Will you help me get this right? I don't think we get a second chance on this one."`,
