        story: `"The storm has passed. We're all safe — thank you for asking, Hina made sure to tell me to say that. But here's the problem: I no longer know which way is home. There's no compass like yours out here — only memory, stars, and skill passed down through generations. This is wayfinding, properly, for the first time. Help me remember everything Hina taught me, because right now my mind feels as empty as the horizon."`,
