        journalWakes: `A seasonal wheel appears beside the star map. <em>"That actually makes so much sense now. I feel like I understand the sky better than I ever have in my whole life, and that's entirely down to you.<br><br>Now I understand the turning sky. One thing remains — a tool to bring it all together. Hina mentioned something about a strange new instrument some traders carry. I'm curious. Probably shouldn't be, but I am."</em>`,
